    "description": "Dongeng Bayang Kulit is a turn-based RPG that is loosely based on Southeast Asian folklore. Join the recently ship-less, Captain N'man and his mystical guide, Putri Matami as they travel in search for answers regarding a mysterious apparition that has taken to incessantly haunting N'man. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/2614f639b310649eab1503afaf628854.avif?t=1685801402\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>What grudge does the spirit haunting N'man hold? What will it take to free N'man of this curse? You'll have to play to find out! We hope you have a great experience with it!<br><br><br>Gameplay features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Narrative-free, yet detailed story - Rich story and lore buried in any and all items you are able to pick up. Put it aside, or delve deep into it at your leisure! Heavily inspired by local Southeast Asian folk tales.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/93fd8f808487b094a7c2fc3807dd867c.poster.avif?t=1685801402\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/93fd8f808487b094a7c2fc3807dd867c.webm?t=1685801402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/93fd8f808487b094a7c2fc3807dd867c.mp4?t=1685801402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Simple, yet brutal combat - Set up your abilities, plan the most efficient way to overcome those who would dare stand in your way! Or fail and be punished heavily.. What cannot act, cannot hurt you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/1c572b4095d1e1a925a43a660abb3e9c.poster.avif?t=1685801402\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/1c572b4095d1e1a925a43a660abb3e9c.webm?t=1685801402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/1c572b4095d1e1a925a43a660abb3e9c.mp4?t=1685801402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Parallax mapped environments - Hand-drawn maps that allows for more organic and atmospheric areas. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/0d23d0d1f9e566dba34780d26dd9ad4d.poster.avif?t=1685801402\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/0d23d0d1f9e566dba34780d26dd9ad4d.webm?t=1685801402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295930/extras/0d23d0d1f9e566dba34780d26dd9ad4d.mp4?t=1685801402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traditional themed score - A score that focuses on traditional brass percussions, ethnic guitars, and local drums - but used in a modern way that's almost inadvisable!</li></ul>",
